## LLMClient

```ts
interface LLMCallParams {
  messages: StandardMessage[]
  tools?: StandardTool[]
  model: { provider: 'anthropic' | 'openai' | 'gemini' | 'grok', modelId: string }
  maxTokens?: number
  temperature?: number
}

interface StandardResponse {
  content: string | null
  toolCalls?: ToolCall[]
  usage: { inputTokens: number, outputTokens: number }
  stopReason: 'end_turn' | 'tool_use' | 'max_tokens'
}
```

Cada adapter traduce `StandardMessage[]` y `StandardTool[]` al formato del provider, hace la llamada HTTP, y normaliza la respuesta a `StandardResponse`.

### AnthropicAdapter
- Usa `@anthropic-ai/sdk`
- Mapea `tool_use` / `tool_result` a roles de Anthropic

### OpenAIAdapter
- Usa `openai` SDK
- `baseURL` configurable para Grok (`https://api.x.ai/v1`)

### GeminiAdapter
- Usa `@google/generative-ai`
- Traduce `contents[]` y `functionDeclarations`

