## Endpoints internos de Laravel (solo para el worker)

```
GET  /api/v1/assistant/internal/unprocessed-messages/{userId}
GET  /api/v1/assistant/internal/memories/{userId}
PUT  /api/v1/assistant/internal/memories/{userId}/{category}
POST /api/v1/assistant/internal/mark-processed
```

Autenticados con `ASSISTANT_SERVICE_TOKEN`. Middleware `AssistantServiceAuth`.

